{"tid":987673,"cid":12,"subCid":0,"title":"（講故）平安夜上咗女同事屋企洗廁所","createTime":"2019-01-19T13:25:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-17T13:29:01.000Z","uid":31827,"like":122,"dislike":58,"uniUserReply":59,"replies":[{"pid":"e465f5dd55858bc01f27ae24223008fb28619bdc","tid":987673,"uid":31827,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-19T13:25:09.000Z","msg":"以下故事都係虛構<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n引子：<br />\n是咁的，今日趁住聖誕假約左班同事一齊上其中一個屋企到玩，在場計埋我有五男四女。我地呢幾個係公司都特別friend，平時都會一齊lunch咁。<br />\n<br />\n話說一開頭都正正常常玩下poker同大食會，之後開始有人拎啲酒出黎，玩酒game。<br />\n<br />\n其中一個屋主加搞手係mc，其餘就一男一女咁分隊，我同另一位女同事joyce一組。佢平時份人好brother，冇咩港女性格，我心諗今次part佢實贏硬啦。<br />\n<br />\n咩乒乓波，抽啤牌都冇咩問題。大家開始飲多兩杯之後就黎料。因為輸左gmae要大懲罰，食果啲垃圾燒蟲。<br />\n<br />\n最後一個遊戲係要輪住玩鬥快講三樣野，我成日輸，但係佢都冇放棄我。<br />\n<br />\nJoyce話：「你個老鼠屎，輸左你聽日上黎幫我洗廁所。」<br />\n<br />\n我：「放心，一定贏。」<br />\n<br />\n點知我地最後真係輸左。我本身諗想幫佢頂左啲蟲佢，點知佢一口就食左，根本就唔驚，反而係我搞左好耐連水吞，我仲好似聽到佢話我冇撚用。<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁呢件事本來諗住就咁完，因為佢地幾個女仔話要11點就走，咁我地班男仔就繼續有下場，係到訓。<br />\n<br />\n事情就黎喇，正當我以為冇事既時候，Joyce突然send個whatsapp比我，提我聽日記得上佢屋企洗廁所。<br />\n<br />\n我已經read左，到宜家都仲未敢覆佢，到底應該點做好<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我本黎以為講笑，但佢好似好認真咁。一場同事，我都唔想搞到咁僵。洗個廁所其實我都接受到，只不過我驚其實佢係講笑，得我認真，到時比佢笑到面黃。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：上去洗啦男人老狗驚咩<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：傻仔人地講笑咋"},{"pid":"98e4c3a7757845643ac4f9f000353dc4a68b248e","tid":987673,"uid":67896,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-19T13:26:15.000Z","msg":"捨得出故啦咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac76793220a8973b1699d5c23d46440cf624b0a4","tid":987673,"uid":31827,"like":7,"dislike":7,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-19T13:26:51.000Z","msg":"原文可以去呢到睇：<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/953048/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/953048/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n支持小弟創作，請follow我ig<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">IG:silvergrey0213</span></span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/silvergrey0213/?hl=en\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fsilvergrey0213%2F%3Fhl%3Den&d=LhHcmVfiNK42SI8LqBdBTrIOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=7b5f7e80\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/silvergrey0213/?hl=en</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n可以追返以前的故事：<br />\n《執行者》（已出書）<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/670661/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/670661/page/1</a><br />\n《曖昧是相愛中最幸福的階段》（已完結）<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.shikoto.com/articles/16170.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.shikoto.com%2Farticles%2F16170.html&d=LhHcmVfiNK42SI8LqBdBTrIOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=efe051d9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.shikoto.com/articles/16170.html</a><br />\n<br />\n《女神話贏左遊戲，就真空同我出一日街》（已完結）<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.shikoto.com/articles/91890.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.shikoto.com%2Farticles%2F91890.html&d=LhHcmVfiNK42SI8LqBdBTrIOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=6947a170\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.shikoto.com/articles/91890.html</a><br />\n<br />\n《這之後，我們班獲得了殺戮的能力》（已完結）<a href=\"https://www.shikoto.com/articles/157173.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.shikoto.com%2Farticles%2F157173.html&d=LhHcmVfiNK42SI8LqBdBTrIOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=20008655\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.shikoto.com/articles/157173.html</a>"},{"pid":"bb704a3cfa42198e4182b05e2571f702bf715ea7","tid":987673,"uid":31827,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"98e4c3a7757845643ac4f9f000353dc4a68b248e","tid":987673,"uid":67896,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-19T13:26:15.000Z","msg":"捨得出故啦咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-19T13:27:14.000Z","msg":"可以唔洗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我會改野"},{"pid":"776d5f843c0c9b6aca7edd05655c30df067d3837","tid":987673,"uid":67718,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-19T13:27:26.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"fb28214d15b855716755f2c0f808211bdc7fa6ce","tid":987673,"uid":172823,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-19T13:28:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"916635503ffd2546465d2b16245a32250344f01a","tid":987673,"uid":167260,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-19T13:29:11.000Z","msg":"屌"},{"pid":"ba6b743d54b882ade001ded9a6423b81635d92d4","tid":987673,"uid":67896,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"bb704a3cfa42198e4182b05e2571f702bf715ea7","tid":987673,"uid":31827,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"98e4c3a7757845643ac4f9f000353dc4a68b248e","tid":987673,"uid":67896,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-19T13:26:15.000Z","msg":"捨得出故啦咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-19T13:27:14.000Z","msg":"可以唔洗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我會改野"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-19T13:29:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1944826ecc6e343037564c2bae805dc65999b8c0","tid":987673,"uid":167260,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-19T13:30:13.000Z","msg":"樓主又痴咗線。。。"},{"pid":"2dc8f9182a0a68023d0cddc7a9d64d3e132e1794","tid":987673,"uid":31827,"like":30,"dislike":3,"score":27,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-19T13:37:51.000Z","msg":"是咁的，24號當日，因為當到神蹟的鼓勵，我決定還是上去一探究竟。<br />\n<br />\n我最擔心的是這一切只是個玩笑，又或者是惡作劇，如果我起了異心，就會有慘烈的下場。因此，我必須採取可攻可守的方法。<br />\n<br />\n在出發之前，我透過whatsapp再一次刺探一下joyce的口風。<br />\n<br />\n「我岩岩先起身咋，你幾時過黎呀？」joyce是認真的，並不是因為昨晚喝醉才亂說話。因此，我又再追問：<br />\n<br />\n「咁我洗唔洗帶野上黎？」出於禮貌，這也是有必要的。<br />\n<br />\n怎料joyce卻說：「我屋企冇人，咩都唔洗帶呀。」<br />\n<br />\n屋企冇人。<br />\n<br />\n屋企冇人。<br />\n<br />\n屋企冇人。<br />\n<br />\n我腦海不斷徘徊這句話。不過joyce是個粗神經的人，可能沒有留意到這句話的魔力吧。<br />\n<br />\n又或者，這才是她真正的目的。<br />\n<br />\nJoyce是我喜歡的類型<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，眼睛大大，皮膚黝黑，喜歡做運動，給人一種正面、陽光的感覺。而且她很容易相處，所以朋友也很多。<br />\n<br />\n我就是其中一位。<br />\n<br />\n最重要的是，因為長期運動，所以joyce也有一雙長美腿。平日上班要求女同事要穿西裙，所以我們一眾男同事就可以大飽眼福了。<br />\n<br />\nJoyce是一位極可愛的女生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，追她的男同事也不少，我一直不覺得自己會成功，所以沒有信心進擊。更因為這樣，我才覺得這次洗廁所的事件是假的。"},{"pid":"c64bf0f8d8099e573c9328c41687921b64f97010","tid":987673,"uid":226020,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-19T13:44:20.000Z","msg":"加速<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80b61d8fc74c7f7c6df0b1f6b4e85d56c528bece","tid":987673,"uid":176405,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-19T13:59:29.000Z","msg":"LM"},{"pid":"1bbd1304095446090a28d98fd427d19eacf3449f","tid":987673,"uid":828,"like":32,"dislike":2,"score":30,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-19T14:04:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n補返張腳圖代入下先啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6384b0d6eef4b37a775f1d7c96b3b46118a8fb68","tid":987673,"uid":67896,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"1bbd1304095446090a28d98fd427d19eacf3449f","tid":987673,"uid":828,"like":32,"dislike":2,"score":30,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-19T14:04:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n補返張腳圖代入下先啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-19T14:13:26.000Z","msg":"好波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7bf310a3082cc7dc21f7fc4c31c48e6991050504","tid":987673,"uid":31827,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"1bbd1304095446090a28d98fd427d19eacf3449f","tid":987673,"uid":828,"like":32,"dislike":2,"score":30,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-19T14:04:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n補返張腳圖代入下先啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-19T14:14:13.000Z","msg":"屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"417e1b8178351a99070c18621361c32890686fe7","tid":987673,"uid":43845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7bf310a3082cc7dc21f7fc4c31c48e6991050504","tid":987673,"uid":31827,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"1bbd1304095446090a28d98fd427d19eacf3449f","tid":987673,"uid":828,"like":32,"dislike":2,"score":30,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-19T14:04:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n補返張腳圖代入下先啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-19T14:14:13.000Z","msg":"屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-19T14:32:1